522
00:35:53,907 --> 00:35:56,348
To je tvoj predpoklad.

523
00:35:56,478 --> 00:35:57,547
Čože?

524
00:35:57,548 --> 00:35:59,061
Prepáč.

525
00:35:59,447 --> 00:36:02,287
