Nie sme tu len my dvaja.

592
00:40:09,768 --> 00:40:10,798
Čože?

593
00:40:12,408 --> 00:40:14,951
Ostávajú tu ľudia.

594
00:40:15,477 --> 00:40:17,537
Vidím ich.

595
00:40:28,561 --> 00:40:33,561
